Installation:

Open the command prompt
Execute: dotnet tool install --global SpecFlow.Plus.LivingDoc.CLI
Restart the command prompt
Execute: livingdoc --version

Report Generation:

Open the command prompt
Execute: cd C:/<workspace-path>/<project-path>/bin/Debug/netcoreapp3.1
Execute: livingdoc test-assembly <project-name>.dll -t TestExecution.json
Open the generated html file in the browser
Note: Generate the report only after executing the tests.
